{"tid":1631011,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"其實大遊行有問題 唔關地區事","createTime":"2019-10-06T14:24:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-06T15:53:44.000Z","uid":222190,"like":10,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"4bf00ad8b79b385d2eef68a53e06089d1c0383a5","tid":1631011,"uid":222190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T14:24:28.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: orange;\">請大家注意自己態度<br />\n檢討問題後 加以改善<br />\n停止分化 互罵</span><br />\n<br />\n好多人檢討後都話 港島唔適合勇武<br />\n根據過往被捕人數就知<br />\n應該分散各區出擊<br />\n這個的確係事實 港島比班狗玩熟晒<br />\n對我地好不利<br />\n- - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - -<br />\n個人結論：<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">大遊行只適合 和理非參與(不論港島or九龍區)</span><br />\n目的打國際線 文宣<br />\n大遊行 有大量和理非 「做後勤」<br />\n其實會影響勇武行動<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">所以遊行後應流水式散去 期間唔好停係度撩狗</span><br />\nsuch as 金鐘夏慤道 <br />\n重複，大遊行唔好再撩狗 要勇武先離開大遊行<br />\n但往往大遊行 都同勇武掛勾<br />\n可能大家要適應下<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">香港人 反抗</span></span>"},{"pid":"39aff0dde837b71caa34f9e32c022c171d8cc32f","tid":1631011,"uid":222190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T14:26:00.000Z","msg":"請大家注意 國際戰線<br />\n<br />\n聯合國人權大佬有嘢講<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1630790\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1630790</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"904b440bdbccced144ffd551032c460e1e22aebf","tid":1631011,"uid":125389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T14:27:56.000Z","msg":"Tui"},{"pid":"572f204b2c5b59a7330d5ad03ceb9015ab83955a","tid":1631011,"uid":222190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T14:31:54.000Z","msg":"請勇武唔好再參加大遊行<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1630596\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1630596</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"c2f011e49c40b7295f844407b0f9feecbaa61c3d","tid":1631011,"uid":222190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T14:32:47.000Z","msg":"<img 